channel.title: Problem with Cache downloading?
channel.description:
Can someone please add me on skype and help me with this? My skype is DigitalPk3r
The cache downloads completely, unpacks and etc but then the client just stops loading. Not sure how else to explain it.

item.title: Problem with Cache downloading?
item.dc:creator: @Slant Slant
item.description:
@Slant wrote:

It could be that you packed your cache wrong. Btw it’s client sided. To pack it correctly you must go into where all your cache files are stored go Ctrl-A then go add to archive .zip upload it to your host and then try it. Tell me if this works, if it doesn’t post a picture of what happens.
